    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve deeper into the Nightmare with the<i> Angel Wings: Endless Night - Supporter Pack </i>(what a name!) This bundle includes a 97-page artbook as well as over 100 4K wallpapers (3840x2160 pixels) from <i>Endless Night</i>. We thank you for all your support!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please note that for Steam Deck users, these features are accessible via Desktop mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200070/extras/75b9fd649054fd00ac59b038edf1d668.avif?t=1730948313\" width=500 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get behind the scenes of<i> Endless Night</i> with an artbook detailing the creation process, as well as providing new insights and lore into the world of <i>Angel Wings</i>. This 97-page artbook (delivered as a PDF to your installation folder) contains character bios, concept art, and previously unseen extras!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200070/extras/398b4db06fe22899ec7c0e98a8275fe6.avif?t=1730948313\" width=470 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200070/extras/e925eecdb7747c1e14e420dc60d630a5.avif?t=1730948313\" width=500 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 4K wallpaper pack contains the vast majority of art in the world of <i>Endless Night</i>, conveniently sorted by chapter and ready for your screen! The wallpaper pack also includes some original compositions ideal for daily desktop use.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200070/extras/92a5593bb7ba87ee8f2d3b66b7aac841.avif?t=1730948313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200070/extras_big/92a5593bb7ba87ee8f2d3b66b7aac841.avif?t=1730948313 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
